narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learnt about key issues in climate change and the research therein. It was an insightful class that encouraged us to question the facts and research and develop critical thinking abilities
Learnt a lot about Climate change economics

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Strengths: covered all major issues in climate change and had healthy discussions Weaknesses: digressed a bit sometimes, could also cover some basic facts before moving on to more complex research
Very engaging and thought provoking course, no changes required

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: yes. Great overall knowledge is developed. Students gain different perspectives on the topic at hand.
I would recommend this course to a student who wants to learn about the latest research in climate change -- it did not have too much Economics per se but many interesting discussions
